commandDescriptions.cmdstats: Get the amount of uses of every command
commandDescriptions.disclaimer: Some basic information about the bot
commandDescriptions.eval: Evaluate JavaScript code with client context (Owner-only)
commandDescriptions.playing: Get the amount of users who are playing a specific game
commandDescriptions.ctgp/recent: Get the recent top CTGP Time Trial uploads. Usage: ctgp recent [amount of tracks to show]
commandDescriptions.ctgp/stats: CTGP statistics such as uploaded ghosts, leaderboards etc.
commandDescriptions.mkw/list: Gives the amount of available mario kart wii rooms (worldwide, continental and private)
commandDescriptions.mkw/regions: Gives the amount of players logged in from different login regions
commandDescriptions.mkw/user: Gives information about a player (has to be in a room): VR, BR, connection issues etc.
commandDescriptions.mkw/users: Gives a list of players that are in rooms
commandDescriptions.mod/ban: Bans a GuildMember. (Target can be expressed by passing a user ID, a user tag (User#1234) or by mentioning them
commandDescriptions.mod/softban: Softbans a GuildMember. (Bans and unbans a member. Its purpose is to delete all recent messages.
commandDescriptions.mod/unban: Unbans a specific user. User can be specified by using its ID.
commandDescriptions.ssbb/info: Get information about super smash bros. brawl rooms
commandDescriptions.tag/list: Gives a list with most-used tags
commandDescriptions.tag/transfer: (deactivated) Transfer a tag to another user
